OL,3,CDaughter admits trying to smother mum
OL,4,Cin 'attempted mercy killing'
OL,6,FA woman has admitted trying to smother
OL,7,Fher elderly mother with a pillow in
OL,8,Fher hospital bed.
OL,10,FA court heard Susan Hardwick, 64,
OL,11,Fcarried out an "attempted mercy
OL,12,Fkilling" as she believed her mother,
OL,13,FJoan Hardwick, 89, was going to be
OL,14,Ftransferred to a hospital for
OL,15,Fpalliative care where she had
OL,16,Fpreviously received poor care.
OL,18,FAn earlier hearing was told Joan
OL,19,FHardwick was receiving end-of-life
OL,20,Fcare at Doncaster Royal Infirmary at
OL,21,Fthe time of the incident on 24 July.
