OL,3,CDaughter admits trying to smother mum
OL,4,Cin 'attempted mercy killing'
OL,6,FSusan Hardwick was visibly emotional
OL,7,Fas she pleaded guilty to attempted
OL,8,Fmurder at Sheffield Crown Court on
OL,9,FMonday.
OL,11,FHer basis of plea, read in court,
OL,12,Fsaid: "At the time of the incident the
OL,13,Fdefendant was suffering from
OL,14,Fdepression and anxiety through being
OL,15,Fseparated from her mother ` they had
OL,16,Fnever been apart.
OL,18,F"She understood her mother was about
OL,19,Fto be transferred to another hospital
OL,20,Fto undergo palliative care."
