OL,3,CDaughter admits trying to smother mum
OL,4,Cin 'attempted mercy killing'
OL,6,FThe court heard Susan Hardwick, who
OL,7,Fhas "significant" mental health
OL,8,Fproblems, "feared her mother would die
OL,9,Falone and in discomfort" at the other
OL,10,Fhospital and the incident was
OL,11,F"consistent with an attempted mercy
OL,12,Fkilling".
OL,14,FShe told a witness she was going to
OL,15,Fkill her mother and then kill herself,
OL,16,Fa judge was told.
