OL,3,CDaughter admits trying to smother mum
OL,4,Cin 'attempted mercy killing'
OL,6,FThe court heard Joan Hardwick, who was
OL,7,Falso found with a cut to the back of
OL,8,Fher neck after the incident, is now in
OL,9,Fa care home and was "anxious" to see
OL,10,Fher daughter, particularly as her 90th
OL,11,Fbirthday is coming up in August.
OL,13,FJudge Jeremy Richardson lifted a
OL,14,Frestraining order restricting Susan
OL,15,FHardwick's contact with her mother,
OL,16,Fand bailed her until her sentencing
OL,17,Fhearing on 29 September.
